overview.en: SZH is a super intelligent ledger of data, as well as a sub-chain of SMA used in artificial intelligence token, serving the main chain of ecology, SMA, SZH can be equivalent replacement SMA, SZH is mainly used in the platform of mall currency source circulation, project incubation and dividends and other ways to achieve economic sharing.
overview.zh: SZH是数据超级智能账本，同样也是SMA的子链运用于人工智能代币，服务于生态内的主链SMA，SZH可等价置换SMA，SZH主要用于平台的商城币源流通，项目孵化和分红等多种途径，实现经济共享。
